English Version:

All images in this repository are licensed under [LICENSE](./LICENSE). Provided that you comply with the following terms, you are free to use, modify, and create derivative works of these materials:  
  - Share — You may copy and redistribute these materials in any medium or format.  
  - Adapt — You may remix, transform, and build upon the materials.

However, you must adhere to the following conditions:  
  - If used online — When using the materials for online content such as posts, blogs, or similar, you must retain the original creator attribution included in the images.  
  - If used in formal publications — When using the materials in academic papers, books, or other formal publications, please cite the source in the reference section using the citation format specified by this repository; in such cases, the original creator attribution in the images may be removed.  
  - Non-commercial use — You may not use these materials for any direct commercial purposes.

